72
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:50,930
Let's quickly get some water and go back upstairs.

73
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:59,110
Chairman, good morning.

74
00:04:59,110 --> 00:05:03,170
Are you going to work already?

75
00:05:03,170 --> 00:05:06,570
Yes, I have a breakfast meeting today.

76
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:11,660
Chairman, I came home very late yesterday.

77
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:14,790
I don't know what time exactly I came home.

78
00:05:14,790 --> 00:05:18,680
I took the last bus and got off at the stop.

79
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:21,320
I remember until then.

80
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:23,470
But I don't remember anything after that.

81
00:05:23,470 --> 00:05:26,290
I think I was blacked out.

82
00:05:26,290 --> 00:05:29,860
I can't remember anything at all.

83
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:32,260
Is that so?

84
00:05:32,260 --> 00:05:34,490
Yes. We found our long-lost aunt.

85
00:05:34,490 --> 00:05:37,950
I got too excited that the whole family gathered in a while.

86
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:40,780
So I think I overly drank a bit.

87
00:05:42,220 --> 00:05:48,490
I hope I didn't do something wrong to you, did I?

88
00:05:50,010 --> 00:05:53,070
You said you don't remember anything because you were blacked out,

89
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:56,420
but I guess you do remember seeing me last night.

90
00:05:56,420 --> 00:05:58,380
No! No, I don't.

91
00:05:58,380 --> 00:06:01,480
I don't remember a thing.

92
00:06:01,510 --> 00:06:05,260
Did I run into you last night?

93
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:07,160
If you don't remember, that's okay.

94
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:11,510
It sounds like you were blacked out last night.

95
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:17,100
Chairman, have a good day.

96
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:21,070
Have a good day as well, Ms. Park.

97
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:31,600
I hope he believes that I don't remember anything.

98
00:06:41,790 --> 00:06:45,780
So she was blacked out.

99
00:06:45,780 --> 00:06:52,140
Chairman, why did I not recognize you when you were the first love that I wanted to see again so badly?

100
00:06:52,140 --> 00:06:58,560
It's because you became so handsome.

101
00:07:16,820 --> 00:07:18,770
Please eat some for yourself, Noona.

102
00:07:18,770 --> 00:07:20,870
