103
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:24,820
Kyung Hoon, I mean Soo Chul.

104
00:07:24,820 --> 00:07:27,620
I get full just watching you eat.

105
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:30,830
Excuse me, can we have some cold buckwheat noodles?

106
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:33,830
I really can't eat anymore. I'm full.

107
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:36,340
But they say there is a separate stomach for cold noodles.

108
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:38,460
You can eat it.

109
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:41,750
