110
00:07:41,750 --> 00:07:44,270
Yes, I am.

111
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:48,760
I am going to give you everything I wanted to feed you until now.

112
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:51,290
Even if you get fat, it doesn't matter.

113
00:07:51,290 --> 00:07:54,990
Oh, Noona.

114
00:07:54,990 --> 00:07:56,710
I forgot about this.

115
00:07:56,710 --> 00:08:00,190
I asked to see you because I wanted to show you this.

116
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:03,640
What is it?

117
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:05,480
Take a look.

118
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:08,130
It's a photo of our mom and dad.

119
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:24,890
Are they my mom and father?

120
00:08:24,930 --> 00:08:27,130
Yes.

121
00:08:27,130 --> 00:08:29,920
They're our mom and dad.

122
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:33,240
Who brought you into this world.

123
00:08:48,620 --> 00:08:51,080
Noona,

124
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:54,420
