125
00:08:54,420 --> 00:08:59,200
Yes. Of course, you can.

126
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:04,040
Father...

127
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:07,770
Kyung Hoon...

128
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:13,640
I'm so sorry.

129
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,620
Kyung Hoon!

130
00:09:15,620 --> 00:09:18,990
Kyung Hoon... Kyung Hoon...

131
00:09:18,990 --> 00:09:21,710
I'm sorry, Kyung Hoon.

132
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:26,620
If I didn't lose you that time...

133
00:09:26,620 --> 00:09:30,890
Mom, I'm sorry.

134
00:09:30,890 --> 00:09:34,160
I'm sorry, Kyung Hoon.

135
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:40,240
Don't cry, I'm sorry.

136
00:09:56,220 --> 00:09:58,320
What is this?

137
00:09:58,320 --> 00:10:00,350
Mom! Mom?

138
00:10:00,350 --> 00:10:02,890
Mom, mom!

139
00:10:02,890 --> 00:10:05,960
What is it? I'm busy working!

140
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:08,490
The balcony here is connected to the neighbor's house!

141
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:11,670
Why is the balcony connected?

142
00:10:11,670 --> 00:10:15,000
Oh, according to the Madam, no, she's my in-law's now.

143
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:18,340
She said they visit each other with the neighbor anytime.

144
00:10:18,340 --> 00:10:20,590
I think they're very close to each other.

145
00:10:20,590 --> 00:10:22,060
With the neighbor?

146
00:10:22,060 --> 00:10:23,980
But how friendly can they be to share a balcony?

147
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:26,630
It's as if it's one house.

148
00:10:28,110 --> 00:10:33,420
