149
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:38,330
Mom, I think sister-in-law's home.

150
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:42,830
- Welcome home!
- Hello, I came together this time.

151
00:10:42,830 --> 00:10:44,810
Lady-in-law and sister-in-law,

152
00:10:44,810 --> 00:10:47,290
what brings you here?

153
00:10:47,290 --> 00:10:49,740
Were you working here?

154
00:10:49,740 --> 00:10:53,420
You're our family now! We need to work harder, then.

155
00:10:53,420 --> 00:10:55,240
No, that's impossible!

156
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:58,780
When I didn't know is one thing, but how can I ask my in-law to work for me?

157
00:10:58,780 --> 00:11:01,630
And it's good that you're here.

158
00:11:01,630 --> 00:11:05,270
I was going to call you, sister-in-law!

159
00:11:05,270 --> 00:11:08,890
Since you're with lady-in-law, let's all go together.

160
00:11:08,890 --> 00:11:12,520
Lady-in-law, let's go.

161
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:15,660
Go where?

162
00:11:15,660 --> 00:11:18,340
How do I look, Mom?
 [Fantom]

163
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:23,220
It's so pretty and elegant!

164
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:25,490
We're trying these on because she told us to,

165
00:11:25,490 --> 00:11:28,370
but should we be buying these?

166
00:11:28,370 --> 00:11:30,340
Look at the price tag!

167
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:32,290
These are very expensive.

168
00:11:32,290 --> 00:11:36,540
She's not going to give these out for free. What should we do?

169
00:11:36,540 --> 00:11:40,360
Right, what kind of money do we have to buy these? We barely have enough to feed ourselves.

170
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:45,090
Mom, let's tell her we had something come up and leave.

171
00:11:45,090 --> 00:11:47,730
Right, I think that's the right thing to do. Go take that off--

172
00:11:47,730 --> 00:11:50,000
Oh, sister-in-law!

173
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,720
Wow! You picked the right ones!

174
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,740
They suit you very well.

175
00:11:54,740 --> 00:11:56,780
You too, Lady-in-law, it looks great on you.

176
00:11:56,780 --> 00:11:59,880
Did you pick some clothes for Soo Chul, Dan Dan, and Dae Beom as well?

177
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:03,240
And why don't you pick some more for your son as well?

178
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:06,920
No, how can we choose more clothes?

179
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:09,080
I'm getting these as a gift for you.

180
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,990
So please feel free and choose anything.

181
00:12:10,990 --> 00:12:13,150
A-A gift?

182
00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:14,860
Of course!

183
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:19,110
You're the one who found my lost brother.

184
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:22,180
What couldn't I do for you?

185
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:26,520
But still, these are so expensive, how can we take them all for free?

186
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:30,410
And our son-in-law Park will say something when he finds out!

187
00:12:30,410 --> 00:12:32,480
Why would he?

188
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,840
We're not strangers anymore.

189
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:37,620
If Soo Chul says something, call me.

190
00:12:37,620 --> 00:12:40,430
I'll talk to him well.

191
00:12:40,430 --> 00:12:44,800
But still, how can we have this all for free...

192
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:47,050
Thank you so much.

193
00:12:47,050 --> 00:12:49,590
Thank you, sister-in-law! I'll wear them well!

194
00:12:49,590 --> 00:12:53,230
Choose some more! Come, choose more.

195
00:12:53,230 --> 00:12:56,800
- Go pick more clothes.
- Shall we?

196
00:12:59,210 --> 00:13:02,600
