199
00:13:09,910 --> 00:13:11,850
Oh, yes.

200
00:13:11,850 --> 00:13:15,090
That sounds right.

201
00:13:15,110 --> 00:13:18,240
If it feels rushed, should we do it next year?

202
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:20,040
We don't mind,

203
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:24,210
but I thought it might not be okay for the bride to age another year.

204
00:13:24,210 --> 00:13:27,270
No, next month sounds fine!

205
00:13:27,270 --> 00:13:29,850
Since it's an unprecedented situation, let's have a small ceremony.

206
00:13:29,850 --> 00:13:35,760
Of course! Who holds such grandiose ceremonies these days?

207
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:38,400
What's going on with Se Ryun?

208
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:40,190
She didn't tell me a single word about this.

209
00:13:40,190 --> 00:13:44,080
Is she doing this because she really wants to get married?

210
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:46,400
It seems like they're meant to be together.

211
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:49,220
Our Kyung Seok insisted on dying single,

212
00:13:49,220 --> 00:13:53,700
but he fell in love at first sight with Se Ryun!

213
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:57,990
I know!

214
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:07,930
Se Ryun, are you sure about getting married?

215
00:14:07,930 --> 00:14:10,190
Are you really going to do it?

216
00:14:10,190 --> 00:14:13,930
Mom, you said it's your wish to get me married.

217
00:14:13,930 --> 00:14:16,560
