224
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:35,000
Then I'm going to arrange your wedding day, okay?

225
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:38,210
Don't say something else later on!

226
00:14:38,210 --> 00:14:41,060
Mom, can you give me your credit card?

227
00:14:41,060 --> 00:14:43,870
- Why do you need my card?
- Why else?

228
00:14:43,870 --> 00:14:46,080
