229
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:48,530
My goodness... Fine.

230
00:14:48,530 --> 00:14:50,100
Here.

231
00:14:50,100 --> 00:14:52,610
Just use it as you wish.

232
00:14:52,610 --> 00:14:56,380
As long as you get married, we can get the shares your father left to you.

233
00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:59,160
Then we don't need to use credit cards with limits,

234
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:03,190
and we don't need to ask your brother for more money.

235
00:15:03,190 --> 00:15:06,090
Mom. I have a plan, so I'll get going first.

236
00:15:06,090 --> 00:15:09,330
- Don't forget to lock the door.
- Hey!

237
00:15:09,330 --> 00:15:13,680
I'm going to tell your brother about setting a wedding day for you.

238
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:17,260
Do what you want to do. I'm leaving!

239
00:15:20,140 --> 00:15:23,890
Why does she look like that when she says she's going to get married?

240
00:15:23,890 --> 00:15:26,740
