241
00:15:26,740 --> 00:15:29,830
No, it's better to make her get married at least like this.

242
00:15:29,830 --> 00:15:34,310
Rather than being with that playboy from that parasite household, this is better.

243
00:15:34,310 --> 00:15:36,560
That's how we can get the shares.

244
00:15:36,560 --> 00:15:40,580
- Thank you!
- Here's your Padak Padak, sweet and salty one!

245
00:15:40,580 --> 00:15:42,520
